originalText.text: Limited product selection, but can always find the basics. Clean store. Very nice people. I have however had more than a couple issues here. If you frequent the 183rd and audobon location you will notice the freezers have issues. I purchased frozen waffles with mold as well as frozen pizza with mold. They have issues with the freezers and move food around. Also most items are over priced.
